works.description:
While the audio and track information in this article's copyright lies with myself, the 'Western Highway' title and track lyrics' copyright lie with American artist Gerry O'Beirne. The original permission has expired as of April 2010, and an agreed consensus was arrived at; that this track be removed online. It has since been removed from all sites but this.

I have previously requested removal from the site owners, and while they mean no harm and sought only to promote me, I feel I have exhausted all avenues but this in requesting the page be removed.
